<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM4.10">
<l>umpa rulakāṇ ṭorukuṭaikkī ḻuruppacitaṉ</l>
<l>ṉampoṟ kalaiyalkuṟ peṟṟālu mātariyēṉ</l>
<l>cempavaḷa vāyāṉ tiruvēṅ kaṭameṉṉum</l>
<l>emperumāṉ poṉmalaimē lētēṉu māvēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even if, reigning over the celestial world under a single [royal] parasol,</l>
<l rend="indent">I get Ūrvaśī’s beautiful waist with a gold girdle,</l>
<l>I will not wish for [them].</l>
<l>I will become anything on the golden mountain called the sacred Veṅkaṭa,</l>
<l rend="indent">of our Lord, He with red coral lips.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
